{"tid":979646,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"埋怨人地之前應該要先反省自己","createTime":"2019-01-12T22:38:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-13T04:16:04.000Z","uid":65256,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"223dd45dacc12e441f792e012d550f31149eece6","tid":979646,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T22:38:31.000Z","msg":"每件事發生都必然有佢既原因<br />\n反省自己最重要既係首先要知自己邊度做得唔好<br />\n人地有咁既反應係出於啲咩原因<br />\n清楚了解自己既唔好之後<br />\n就係要諗點樣改<br />\n改左令人唔鍾意自己既缺點<br />\n而且亦真係要付諸行動 儘量唔好再犯<br />\n當你真係有做到上面呢啲野既時候<br />\n如果人地都係咁對你你先好去怨人<br />\n一發生啲咩事永遠唔諗原因就走去怨人既人<br />\n或者自以為自己已經好好 咩都係人地唔好既人<br />\n只會令身邊既人同佢既相處好辛苦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9b0c59a005b4248131192e45724f502b24d552d","tid":979646,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T22:39:52.000Z","msg":"知道"},{"pid":"2577969cf09c12b08f3471a2ea077f5e27345e90","tid":979646,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9b0c59a005b4248131192e45724f502b24d552d","tid":979646,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T22:39:52.000Z","msg":"知道"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T22:40:59.000Z","msg":"孺子可教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6048649fc2b309b8c22a5bbdc80b3dd916c6ac48","tid":979646,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2577969cf09c12b08f3471a2ea077f5e27345e90","tid":979646,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9b0c59a005b4248131192e45724f502b24d552d","tid":979646,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T22:39:52.000Z","msg":"知道"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T22:40:59.000Z","msg":"孺子可教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T22:41:40.000Z","msg":"快來調教我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba0bdb4df4a7819a100c1397e3e91b23a37f59a7","t